{"tid":502697,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做飲食業慘過食屎","createTime":"2017-12-18T07:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T18:53:58.000Z","uid":28309,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d1df9f1be43ec51ec7a9963cc38168027ffe55","tid":502697,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"人工低又多野做<br />\n有啲客又會覺得自己高人一等咁<br />\n真係兩面做人難 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cae70aed230c0fdf95e36b33fa11e9a0918d06","tid":502697,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"我遇過個女侍應<br />\n間野就爆到塞滿人,好似唔休做咁個個失哂明<br />\n豆撚左十幾分先豆到佢埋黎落單...點知一落佢就起哂鋼咁:<br />\n<br />\n「你講慢d,我寫緊」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我fd都呆撚左<br />\n我應佢<br />\n「哦,唔緊要,你慢慢」<br />\n<br />\n之後先好返聲氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bd71d0f366c284cc11222e76a2ca8c7c7183a7","tid":502697,"uid":49738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T08:52:27.000Z","msg":"做樓面又要俾客屌又要俾廚房佬屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224051cb5ba6bfca839549d41588a62c47413ee5","tid":502697,"uid":123511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工低又多野做<br />\n有啲客又會覺得自己高人一等咁<br />\n真係兩面做人難 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最撚麻煩係個啲揀位坐 <br />\n你老母兩條友話我要坐四人卡位<br />\n平日冇乜人都由尻你<br />\n禮拜六日你都咁搞真係屌尻你<br />\n<br />\n仲有送餐 送埋去擺低<br />\n大大聲問 呢個係乜黎<br />\n你老母個分別係大到 紅湯 白湯咁撚樣<br />\n唔撚係個啲少辣 走辣<br />\n仲有你自己落單嗌左啲咩自己唔撚知既<br />\n<br />\n閪客真係搞唔撚掂"},{"pid":"9b2eaba618f852b30442ae1ca73bc1b797381f4b","tid":502697,"uid":58353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔做過飲食業唔好話自己捱過苦<br />\n做開office 而家轉第二份工中間空檔期<br />\n貪得意做下餐飲part time當感受下<br />\n由收銀到執貨 執枱沖野飲煮野食洗爐鏟冰切野倒垃圾洗油槽<br />\n冰火交融 上刀山落油鑊 做到積咁<br />\n仲要遇著香港最多既閪客<br />\n催野食又要求多到成間鋪服侍佢一個咁<br />\n都係得丁屎咁多人工 <br />\n而家心態上同理左 自己係餐廳叫野食對侍應態度都好d<br />\n前後一定講唔該 自己好受佢又好受 因為自己做過明白有幾辛苦<br />\n<br />\n不過飲食業都好多好人 唔會持住老屎忽對你指指點點 多數都對新入職當仔咁教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我比較年輕啦 同埋大家都求打返開心工啫<br />\n<br />\n都遇好既客 唔小心倒瀉野 倒左少少落佢件衫 但佢都一直話唔緊要 個下好似發夢咁"},{"pid":"5e0c7f92643715a9226232cc5e6a9b68a0ec6cb6","tid":502697,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"廚房仔留名"},{"pid":"32c501dca7e9ec7fd8a650b3a2cdb37c48e4e99a","tid":502697,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"係香港打乜工都慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c07e8ebf8d956c66f8778fc8067998ba3a8c72","tid":502697,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"全世界做飲食業最難頂的地方會唔會係香港"},{"pid":"36936e843a177ed6c911f38107405090ea15499d","tid":502697,"uid":116578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"飲食人工其實唔算低 起碼包你唔會餓親<br />\n利申 18開始做pt"},{"pid":"ec602f58bf4527b9acf7fc9c11fc031294ed166e","tid":502697,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T18:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲食人工其實唔算低 起碼包你唔會餓親<br />\n利申 18開始做pt</blockquote><br />\n屌你不如講下返咁既工時做邊行會餓親啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/